Installation
------------
In the php.ini file:
- make sure that always_populate_raw_post_data = On
- Soap server and Soap client must be enabled
- soap.wsdl_cache = 1

Copy opensearch.ini_INSTALL to opensearch.ini and edit it to reflect your setup

Copy opensearch.wsdl_INSTALL to opensearch.wsdl and modify 
the location of the service (at the end of the file)
